  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nIs the ratio 5:10 proportional to 1:2?\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\n5:10 divided by 5 gives 1:2. Thus, they are same to each other. So we can say that 5:10 is proportional to 1:2.",
